The action in the main clause, @V2{{}}, is the more emphasised of the two.

<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{sound^music}}wo@KJ{{hear}}ki@EM{{nagara}}@KJ{{eat^matter}}shimasu.}}
  </td> </tr>
