  </td> </tr>
</table>
<p>

@BGRNDEND{{}}

<h2> Notes </h2>

<p>
@HI{{@EM{{nagara}}}} expresses the fact that an action occurs at the same time as another action.
The action marked by @HI{{@EM{{nagara}}}} is the secondary action.
</p>

<p>
If the subjects of the two verbs are different, @HI{{@EM{{nagara}}}} cannot be used.
A possible alternative in this case would be <a href="grammar-aida.html">@HI{{aida}}</a>.
</p>

